[center][size=25pt]Project- ID Client[/size][/center]
[center]Project ID will need some help and people to register on my forums![/center]
[center]Project ID needs good client coders[/center]
[center]Project- ID needs YOU![/center]
[center]Welcome to project ID development page Hope you enjoy the fetures we are going to bring you i am starting a development team to code project ID -it will have possibally all items all object and all monsters some fun and a fully working 471 game frame[/center]
We need a good client to start off on as that would help us alot anyone who is up for letting me and the development team have an open source client would be wonderfull!
[center][size=25pt]ONLY TRUSTED PEOPLE WILL BEABLE TO JOIN[/size][/center]
[center]Trusted people[/center] [center] -sanga282 -Ragean -dog eats dog -digzey - - - - - -[/center]
[center][size=25pt]TESTERS WILL BE NEEDED![/size][/center]
[center]TESTERS[/center] [center] -xRedemptionx -playermanny2 -jm2k -M00 M00 Pk - - - - - -[/center]
